description: "A late 18th century maritime map of Southeast Asia, marked with expedition routes including the return of Captain Cook’s HMS Endeavour from Australia in 1770, and Captain Philip Carteret’s circumnavigation expedition in 1768."
title: "A   new   chart   of   the   Oriental   Seas   and   Islands   ...   from   the   Isle   of   Ceylon   to   Amoye   in   China"
